autocomplete

Class AutocompleteGUI.AutocompletePanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    Enclosing class:
    AutocompleteGUI

    private class AutocompleteGUI.AutocompletePanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    The panel that interfaces with the Autocomplete object. It consists of a search bar that text can be entered into, and a drop-down list of suggestions auto-completing the user's query.
